---
title: Caribbean-Style Chicken with Jewelled Rice and Lime Mayo
description: Our favourite way of bringing Caribbean flair to a weeknight chicken dish? A sprinkle of jerk seasoning! Zucchini, sweet peppers, corn and lime mayo add a hint of brightness to bring it all together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-a-la-caribeenne-9a899347.jpg
